700908f-a.title: Bronx: Mosholu Parkway Sout - Grand Concourse
700908f-a.text:
East Mosholu Parkway South, south side, east from Grand Concourse, to Van Cortlandt Ave.34.showing an Italian garden in an interior court of the Pickwick Arms; large triangular apartment building.
About 1925.
Browning Studios.
700908f-a.folder: Mosholu Parkway Sout & Grand Concourse, Bronx, NY

700909f-a.title: Bronx: Mosholu Parkway Sout - Grand Concourse
700909f-a.text:
East Mosholu Parkway South (left), south side, east from Grand Concourse to Van Cortlandt Ave. East, showing the Pickwick Arms. The building occupies the triangular block bounded on the east by Grand Concourse (right); on the south by Van Cortlandt Ave. East, and on the
west by East Mosholu Parkway South.
About 1925.
Browning Studios.
